Detailed Table Specifications
1. users (Authentication)
id (UUID, Primary Key)
email (String, Unique)
password_hash (String)
created_at (Timestamp)
updated_at (Timestamp)
2. tasks (Core task management)
id (UUID, Primary Key)
user_id (UUID, Foreign Key → users.id)
title (String, Required)
description (Text, Optional)
priority (Enum: 'low', 'medium', 'high')
tags (JSON Array or Text)
estimated_duration (Integer, minutes)
deadline (Timestamp, Optional)
completed (Boolean, Default: false)
completed_at (Timestamp, Optional)
created_at (Timestamp)
scheduled_time (String, HH:MM format, Optional)
scheduled_date (Date, Optional)
actual_duration (Integer, minutes, Optional)
routine_id (UUID, Foreign Key → routines.id, Optional)
is_recurring (Boolean, Default: false)
parent_recurring_id (UUID, Foreign Key → tasks.id, Optional)
3. recurring_patterns (Recurring task configuration)
id (UUID, Primary Key)
task_id (UUID, Foreign Key → tasks.id)
type (Enum: 'daily', 'weekly', 'monthly')
interval (Integer, every X days/weeks/months)
days_of_week (JSON Array, for weekly patterns)
end_date (Date, Optional)
max_occurrences (Integer, Optional)
4. routines (Task routine templates)
id (UUID, Primary Key)
user_id (UUID, Foreign Key → users.id)
name (String, Required)
description (Text, Optional)
created_at (Timestamp)
5. routine_tasks (Template tasks within routines)
id (UUID, Primary Key)
routine_id (UUID, Foreign Key → routines.id)
title (String, Required)
description (Text, Optional)
priority (Enum: 'low', 'medium', 'high')
tags (JSON Array or Text)
estimated_duration (Integer, minutes)
deadline (Timestamp, Optional)
scheduled_time (String, HH:MM format, Optional)
scheduled_date (Date, Optional)
is_recurring (Boolean, Default: false)
recurring_pattern (JSON, Optional)
6. mood_entries (Daily mood tracking)
id (UUID, Primary Key)
user_id (UUID, Foreign Key → users.id)
date (Date, Unique per user per day)
mood (Enum: 'very-happy', 'happy', 'neutral', 'sad', 'very-sad')
energy (Enum: 'high', 'medium', 'low')
notes (Text, Optional)
created_at (Timestamp)
7. wellness_breaks (Completed wellness activities)
id (UUID, Primary Key)
user_id (UUID, Foreign Key → users.id)
date (Date)
break_type (String, e.g., 'stretching', 'hydration', etc.)
duration (Integer, minutes)
completed_at (Timestamp)
8. focus_sessions (Focus timer sessions)
id (UUID, Primary Key)
user_id (UUID, Foreign Key → users.id)
task_id (UUID, Foreign Key → tasks.id, Optional)
duration (Integer, minutes)
session_date (Date)
started_at (Timestamp)
ended_at (Timestamp)
9. day_summaries (Daily analytics and insights)
id (UUID, Primary Key)
user_id (UUID, Foreign Key → users.id)
date (Date, Unique per user per day)
completed_tasks (Integer)
total_tasks (Integer)
focus_time (Integer, minutes)
completion_rate (Decimal, 0-100)
top_category (String)
suggestions (JSON Array or Text)
created_at (Timestamp)